 development. Reads internal Entire docs (agent-guide, checklist, interfaces) and uses the one-pager for all agent-specific details (hook format, transcript location, config structure).\\n\\nRead and follow the implement procedure from `.claude/skills/agent-integration/implementer.md`.\\n\\n**Expected output:** Complete agent package at `cmd/entire/cli/agent/$AGENT_SLUG/` with all tests passing.\\n\\n**Note:** `AGENT.md` is a living document ã Phases 2 and 3 update it when they discover new information during testing or implementation.\\n\\n## Final Validation\\n\\nAfter all three phases, run the complete validation:\\n\\n```bash\\nmise run fmt      # Format\\nmise run lint     # Lint\\nmise run test:ci  # All tests (unit + integration)\\n```\\n\\nSummarize:\\n- Compatibility verdict from Phase 1\\n- Files created in Phases 2 and 3\\n- Test coverage\\n- Any remaining TODOs or gaps\\n\",\"structuredPatch\":[{\"oldStart\":69,\"oldLines\":7,\"newStart\":69,\"newLines\":7,\"lines\":[\" \",\" Read and follow the implement procedure from `.claude/skills/agent-integration/implementer.md`.\",\" \",\"-**Expected output:** Complete agent package at `cmd/entire/cli/agent/$AGENT_SLUG/` with all tests passing.\",\"+**Expected output:** Complete agent package at `cmd/entire/cli/agent/$AGENT_PACKAGE/` with all tests passing.\",\" \",\" **Note:** `AGENT.md` is a living document ã Phases 2 and 3 update it when they discover new information during testing or implementation.\",\" \"]}],\"userModified\":false,\"replaceAll\":false},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"cac124a4-9a55-4397-b4d7-505ce7621fd9\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"71ae9d64-b5a6-4a9b-b771-da384fd8b1af\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/wt/kiro-oneshot\",\"sessionId\":\"c59c11f6-4ea6-4e4a-8ce4-0d1e0a044b00\",\"version\":\"2.1.61\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/kiro-oneshot\",\"slug\":\"snuggly-beaming-peacock\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01PS3F5LemRRR6ENtXUN8U8